719563f-a.title: Manhattan: East River Drive - 60th Street (East)
719563f-a.text:
East River Drive, at the foot of East 60th Street, show-
constructional details of this new marginal thoroughfare.
The view is eastward towards Welfare (Blackwells) Island.
Thereupon appears new hospital facilities. Beyond is Long
Island City and Astoria on the 2ueens shore.
No's. 1-B August 1, 1939
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

719562f-b.title: Manhattan: East River Drive - 60th Street (East)
719562f-b.text:
East River Drive, north from East 0th Street, showing
constructional details of this new marginal highway., In
the background are hospital and laboratory structures. The
latter is the Rockefeller Research and the former, the New
York Hospital-Cornell Medical College Center.
April 10, 1940 No. 2
August 1, 1939 No. 1
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
